            "label": "Explore fast, haul if you like",
            "text": "The Cobra's eight optionals fit a class-4 scoop, Guardian booster, big SRV bay, AFMU and scanner — with room for cargo. Its speed makes in-system work brisk; swap optionals to turn the explorer into a hauler whenever the trip changes."
